<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Konrad VI., Herr von Bickenbach und Burggraf von Miltenberg</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Geleit für die Nürnberger Kaufleute auf dem Weg zu und von der Frankfurter Fastenmesse.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_79" id="39r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_79_r1l29"><expan>Burggraf<ex>en</ex></expan> cʒu <expan>Miltemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> / </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_79_r1l30"><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan> etc <expan>Rog<ex>amus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr vnſer <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd kaufleute / etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_79_r1l31">in die <expan>nehſtkünftig<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>vaſte<ex>n</ex>meſſe</expan> / gen <expan>franck<ex>furt</ex></expan> vnd <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> darauſʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_79_r1l32">mit ſicherm geleite <expan>günſtigliche<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>fürſehe<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllet / <expan>Alsver<ex>re</ex></expan> ewr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_79_r1l33">geleit / vnd gepiet geet / etc vt <expan>ſup<ex>ra</ex></expan> / </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_79" id="39r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Burggraf<ex>en</ex></expan> czu <expan>Miltemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan> etc. <expan>Rog<ex>amus</ex></expan>, daz ir
                        unser <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> und kaufleute etc. in die
                                <expan>nehstkünftig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>vaste<ex>n</ex>messe</expan> gen <expan>Franck<ex>furt</ex></expan>
                        und <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> darausz mit sicherm geleite
                                <expan>günstigliche<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>fürsehe<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllet, <expan>alsver<ex>re</ex></expan>
                        ewr geleit und gepiet geet etc. ut <expan>sup<ex>ra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
